{"id":237150,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-四川什邡市民抗议污染，大批警察与市民/","date":"2012-07-03T10:00:57Z","modified":"2012-07-03T10:00:57Z","title":"维权网 | 四川什邡市民抗议污染，大批警察与市民冲突（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vuOavZA7Cmw/T_K8K4Wzs1I/AAAAAAAAI5o/PZbD5u0yt20/s1600/SAM_0387.JPG\"> </a></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vuOavZA7Cmw/T_K8K4Wzs1I/AAAAAAAAI5o/PZbD5u0yt20/s1600/SAM_0387.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vuOavZA7Cmw/T_K8K4Wzs1I/AAAAAAAAI5o/PZbD5u0yt20/s320/SAM_0387.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WSkk5fUAwtw/T_K8MYLnWeI/AAAAAAAAI5w/DVZTjUmB7xA/s1600/SAM_0388.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WSkk5fUAwtw/T_K8MYLnWeI/AAAAAAAAI5w/DVZTjUmB7xA/s320/SAM_0388.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pGvh7FApRlc/T_K8Or_34VI/AAAAAAAAI54/tmUc2KFoVOs/s1600/SAM_0389.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"196\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pGvh7FApRlc/T_K8Or_34VI/AAAAAAAAI54/tmUc2KFoVOs/s320/SAM_0389.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-d8Ul-t0EGN4/T_K8Qap7SgI/AAAAAAAAI6A/COQBU6aXlmM/s1600/SAM_0392.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"209\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-d8Ul-t0EGN4/T_K8Qap7SgI/AAAAAAAAI6A/COQBU6aXlmM/s320/SAM_0392.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>维权网志愿者亲临现场拍摄的图片</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>（维权网信息员李平报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>四川省德阳什邡市民自发抗议污染环境企业</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>由于当局出动大批武警镇压</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>与市民发生冲突</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>当局使用了催泪瓦斯和震爆弹驱赶市民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>而市民用酒瓶石块砖头还击。据当地抗议市民说：有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多名学生被抓，至少两名死亡，其中一名是学生，官方称有多名警察也受到不同程度的外伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>据了解：这起事件源于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>什邡市为“宏达集团”举行的“钼铜”生产项目开工仪式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>当地群众说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>这个项目起先是没有获得批准的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>后什邡市政府和该企业老板四处活动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>才获得了批准</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>当地群众认为这个企业会造成环境污染</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>殃及子孙后代</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>因此自发起来抗议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>一名群众告诉本网信息员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>七月一日</span><span>大家都很理智</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>参与的人也只有不到一千人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>当地的警察也没有采取过激行为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>由于当局出动了外地武警和防爆警察</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>引起了群众的愤怒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>才使得事件升级</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>开始砸市政府</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>警察则使用催泪瓦斯驱赶群众</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>群众用石块酒瓶等物品还击。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>一位女学生告诉本网信息员说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span>她们周边的学校全部停课参与抗议活动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>有同学被打伤，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多名学生被抓捕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>一位抗议者说：震爆弹使得一位中年男子肠子被炸出来了，送往医院后死亡。一位现场目击的女士告诉本网信息员，她看见一位学生被打死，据说被送往医院停尸房。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点左右，当局增派了武警和防爆警察，列队用盾牌驱赶群众，群众并未散去，继续在远处观望。截止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分</span><span>，双方还在僵持中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>，据当地抗议者说：今天能看到的抗议群众已经不多，广场周边到处都是武警和防爆警察把守路口。群众无法进入广场，分散在各街道路口。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1983343442676014585?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/fc705d08SAM_0387.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}